imdb.plot outline: Cafe' (Lulu Lopez) - Totally obsessed with EVERYTHING nice, shiny, great, fashionable, eclectic. She's an over-the-top Latina with a bit of A.D.D. - but very smart. She's an INFLUENCER. This is important. She name drops and loves to give shout outs to designers whose clothes/jewelry she wears, artists she knows. She's a sports fan and loves good food. Leche' (Ashley North) - The "Straight-man" of the duo. Smart, very knowledgeable in music, fashion and finance. She's from Nashville Royalty and alway has a funny story to tell - especially if it relates to a particular situation she's in at the time. The Yin to the Cafe' Yang. A sounding board to the antics of Cafe'. Not up on all the deep Latin cultural nuances and is always asking, "What's a ______?" She's an INFLUENCER - giving shout outs to and having surprise appearances by her designer, musician, entertainment biz friends.

synopsis:
Cafe' (Lulu Lopez) - Totally obsessed with EVERYTHING nice, shiny, great, fashionable, eclectic. She's an over-the-top Latina with a bit of A.D.D. - but very smart. She's an INFLUENCER. This is important. She name drops and loves to give shout outs to designers whose clothes/jewelry she wears, artists she knows. She's a sports fan and loves good food.Leche' (Ashley North) - The "Straight-man" of the duo. Smart, very knowledgeable in music, fashion and finance. She's from Nashville Royalty and alway has a funny story to tell - especially if it relates to a particular situation she's in at the time. The Yin to the Cafe' Yang. A sounding board to the antics of Cafe'. Not up on all the deep Latin cultural nuances and is always asking, "What's a ______?"
She's an INFLUENCER - giving shout outs to and having surprise appearances by her designer, musician, entertainment biz friends.1 What do rapper DRAKE, Ashley North and Cafe' Con Leche have in common?2 What do Kim Kardashian, Nude Sunbathing, Neopolitan Ice Cream and Cafe' Con Leche have in common?3 As usual, FUN was had by all when Chris Berardo & The Desberardos joined the vivacious ladies of Cafe' Con Leche at The Cutting Room NYC. Created and Produced by Frank J. Fernandez4 Part one of the 2 part season 1 episode featuring the amazing art and fashion designs of Chris Barreto who has designed for Madonna and The Dixie Chicks. With Fashion In The Fast Lane Reporter Delvon Johnson. Created and Produced by Emmy winner Frank J. Fernandez.5 Fashion In The Fast Lane reporter Delvon Johnson hits the streets of Manhattan's Upper East Side for some fashionable fun and games with artist and designer Chris Barreto. Created and Produced by Frank J. Fernandez6 Maya Frank is a NY based actress known for her roles in the movies: American Gangster, Wall Street 2 and The Bounty Hunter, and in the TV series Blue Bloods and Law & Order. Maya discusses her passion for art and her ART FOR CAUSE project. Created and Produced by: Frank J. Fernandez.7 Fashion entrepreneur Catherine Schuller talks about RUNWAY THE REALWAY and the plus sized modeling industry. Created and Produced by: Frank J. Fernandez8 Max Vitelli of Phoenix Wrestling Federation cavorts with Lulu Lopez and Ashley North. Created and Produced by: Frank J. FernandezCurrently Airing on FOOTPRINT.TV
